<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>2025년 We'll CSU 전공체험 운영 결과(학과 안내용)</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --card: #ffffff;
      --line: #d7e3f1;
      --line-soft: #e8f0f7;
      --text: #16324f;
      --muted: #5f7893;
      --blue-1: #0f3d66;
      --blue-2: #215b94;
      --blue-3: #5f89b6;
      --blue-4: #8cb0d4;
      --blue-6: #eef5fb;
      --blue-7: #f6fbff;
      --green-1: #1f6a4a;
      --green-2: #3f9c73;
      --green-3: #e6f5ed;
      --green-4: #f4fbf7;
      --red-1: #9a4242;
      --red-2: #d06b6b;
      --red-3: #fbeaea;
      --red-4: #fff7f7;
      --mint-1: #0f766e;
      --mint-2: #14b8a6;
      --mint-3: #ecfeff;
      --yellow-1: #a16207;
      --yellow-2: #facc15;
      --yellow-3: #fffbea;
      --navy-1: #0a2a4a;
      --shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(17, 53, 93, 0.08);
      --radius: 18px;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Malgun Gothic", "Apple SD Gothic Neo", "Noto Sans KR", Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #eff5fb 0%, #f7fbff 100%);
      color: var(--text);
    }
    .page { display: none; }
    .page.active { display: block; }
    .wrap { max-width: 1440px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 28px 22px 40px; }
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-1), var(--blue-2));
      color: #fff;
      padding: 28px 30px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .hero h1 { margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 30px; letter-spacing: -0.3px; font-weight: 800; }
    .hero p { margin: 0; font-size: 15px; opacity: 0.92; }
    .hero-subline { margin-top: 10px; font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.84); }
    .summary-hero { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px; }
    .summary-hero .hero-copy { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }

    .grid-kpi { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .card { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow); padding: 18px 18px 16px; }
    .kpi-card { padding: 18px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f6fbff 100%); }
    .grid-kpi .kpi-card:not(.clickable) {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f5da8 0%, #0f4c92 52%, #0b3e79 100%);
      border: none;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 28px rgba(15, 61, 102, 0.18);
    }
    .kpi-card.clickable { cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease, border-color 0.18s ease; position: relative; }
    .kpi-card.clickable:hover, .kpi-card.clickable:focus-visible { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(17, 53, 93, 0.12); border-color: #b8d0e7; outline: none; }
    .kpi-card.clickable::after { content: "전체 요약 보기 (클릭)"; display: block; margin-top: 8px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--blue-2); font-weight: 700; }
    .grid-kpi .kpi-card:not(.clickable) .kpi-label,
    .grid-kpi .kpi-card:not(.clickable) .kpi-value,
    .grid-kpi .kpi-card:not(.clickable) .kpi-unit { color: #ffffff; }
    .grid-kpi .kpi-card:not(.clickable) .kpi-label { opacity: 0.9; }
    .kpi-label { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 700; }
    .kpi-value { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--blue-1); letter-spacing: -0.6px; }
    .kpi-unit { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); margin-left: 6px; font-weight: 700; }

    .section-grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr; gap: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .section-grid-2.equal { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .section-title { margin: 0 0 14px 0; font-size: 18px; color: var(--blue-1); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.2px; }
    .subtle { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; }
    .select-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .select-wrap { position: relative; min-width: 320px; }
    .select-wrap::after {
      content: "▾";
      position: absolute;
      right: 14px;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-52%);
      color: var(--blue-2);
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 800;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    select {
      appearance: none;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff, #f7fbff);
      color: var(--text);
      padding: 12px 40px 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      min-width: 320px;
      outline: none;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .summary-box { background: var(--blue-6); border: 1px solid #d8e7f6; border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px; }
    .summary-item { margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .summary-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .summary-label { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--blue-2); margin-bottom: 5px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; }
    .summary-text { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.55; }

    .metric-pair { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .metric-card { padding: 16px; border-radius: 14px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 0%, #f7fbff 100%); border: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .metric-card .label { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--blue-2); margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .metric-card .value { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--blue-1); letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .metric-card .meta { margin-top: 8px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.45; color: var(--muted); }
    .compare-wrap { display: grid; gap: 12px; }
    .compare-item { padding: 14px; border-radius: 14px; background: #fbfdff; border: 1px solid var(--line-soft); }
    .compare-head { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text); }
    .compare-track { height: 12px; background: #eaf2f9; border-radius: 999px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .compare-fill { position: absolute; inset: 0 auto 0 0; width: 0%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--blue-4), var(--blue-2)); border-radius: 999px; }
    .compare-meta { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); }

    .theme-grid { display: grid; gap: 12px; }
    .bar-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr 42px; gap: 10px; align-items: center; font-size: 14px; }
    .bar-label { font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }
    .bar-track { height: 14px; background: #eaf2f9; border-radius: 999px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; }
    .bar-fill { height: 100%; width: 0%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--blue-4), var(--blue-2)); border-radius: 999px; }
    .bar-value { text-align: right; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px; }

    .suggest-box { margin-top: 14px; padding: 14px; border-radius: 14px; border: 1px solid #d7e4f2; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f2f8fe 100%); }
    .suggest-title { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--blue-2); margin-bottom: 6px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; }
    .suggest-text { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.55; }
    .comment-top3 { display: grid; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .comment-pill { padding: 12px 14px; border-radius: 14px; background: #f6fbff; border: 1px solid var(--line); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; }
    .comment-list { border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 14px; background: #fcfeff; max-height: 360px; overflow: auto; padding: 8px 0; }
    .comment-item { padding: 11px 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid #edf3f9; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; }
    .comment-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .empty { padding: 18px 14px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; }

    .positive-panel .section-title { color: var(--green-1); }
    .positive-panel .bar-track { background: #eaf5ef; }
    .positive-panel .bar-fill { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #85c7a3, var(--green-2)); }
    .positive-panel .comment-pill { background: var(--green-4); border-color: #d7ebdf; }
    .positive-panel .comment-list { background: #fcfffd; border-color: #d7ebdf; }
    .positive-panel .comment-item { border-bottom-color: #ebf6ef; }
    .positive-panel .subtle { color: #5a7d69; }

    .negative-panel .section-title { color: var(--red-1); }
    .negative-panel .bar-track { background: #f7e7e7; }
    .negative-panel .bar-fill { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #efb2b2, var(--red-2)); }
    .negative-panel .comment-pill { background: var(--red-4); border-color: #efdddd; }
    .negative-panel .comment-list { background: #fffdfd; border-color: #efdddd; }
    .negative-panel .comment-item { border-bottom-color: #f8eaea; }
    .negative-panel .subtle { color: #8b6666; }
    .negative-panel .suggest-box { border-color: #efdddd; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #fff5f5 100%); }
    .negative-panel .suggest-title { color: var(--red-1); }

    .bottom-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr 0.95fr; gap: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 14px; }
    th, td { padding: 10px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e7eff7; text-align: left; }
    th { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; }
    td.rank { width: 40px; color: var(--blue-2); font-weight: 800; }
    td.num { text-align: right; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; font-weight: 700; }
    .theme-point-list { display: grid; gap: 10px; margin: 14px 0 8px; }
    .theme-chip { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 10px 12px; border-radius: 12px; background: #f6fbff; border: 1px solid var(--line); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; }
    .overall-positive-card { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f4fffd 0%, var(--mint-3) 100%); border-color: #bdece6; }
    .overall-positive-card .section-title { color: var(--mint-1); }
    .overall-positive-card .subtle,
    .overall-positive-card .small-note { color: #3b7d76; }
    .overall-positive-card .theme-chip { background: rgba(20, 184, 166, 0.08); border-color: #bdece6; }
    .overall-negative-card { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fffef4 0%, var(--yellow-3) 100%); border-color: #f4df96; }
    .overall-negative-card .section-title { color: var(--yellow-1); }
    .overall-negative-card .subtle,
    .overall-negative-card .small-note { color: #8a6a17; }
    .overall-negative-card .theme-chip { background: rgba(250, 204, 21, 0.14); border-color: #f4df96; }
    .summary-filter-card { margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .summary-filter-head { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .summary-filter-title { margin: 0; font-size: 18px; color: var(--blue-1); font-weight: 800; }
    .summary-filter-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(6, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 12px; }
    .filter-field { display: grid; gap: 6px; }
    .filter-label { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--blue-2); }
    .summary-filters .select-wrap,
    .summary-filters select { min-width: 0; }
    .summary-filter-reset {
      appearance: none;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f2f8fe 100%);
      color: var(--blue-1);
      padding: 11px 14px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .summary-filter-reset:hover,
    .summary-filter-reset:focus-visible { box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(17, 53, 93, 0.1); outline: none; }
    .summary-table-wrap { overflow: auto; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .summary-table { min-width: 1320px; font-size: 13px; table-layout: auto; }
    .summary-table thead th { position: sticky; top: 0; background: #f3f8fd; z-index: 1; color: var(--blue-2); font-size: 12px; white-space: nowrap; }
    .summary-table tbody tr:nth-child(even) td { background: #fbfdff; }
    .summary-table th, .summary-table td { white-space: nowrap; padding: 12px 14px; }
    .summary-table th:nth-child(5), .summary-table td:nth-child(5) { min-width: 320px; }
    .summary-table th:nth-child(12), .summary-table td:nth-child(12) { min-width: 120px; }
    .small-note { margin-top: 8px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.45; }
    .footer-message { text-align: center; padding: 18px; border-radius: 18px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-1), #0f3d66); color: #ffffff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); box-shadow: 0 16px 28px rgba(10, 42, 74, 0.18); }

    .action-row { display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; gap: 10px; }
    .outline-button {
      appearance: none;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.18s ease, transform 0.18s ease;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .outline-button:hover, .outline-button:focus-visible { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.16); transform: translateY(-1px); outline: none; }
    .summary-card { padding: 0; overflow: hidden; }
    .summary-card-header { padding: 18px 20px 0; }
    .summary-card-title { margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 18px; color: var(--blue-1); font-weight: 800; }
    .summary-card-subtitle { display: none; }

    @media (max-width: 1200px) {
      .grid-kpi, .section-grid-2, .bottom-grid, .summary-filter-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .metric-pair { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .summary-hero { flex-direction: column; }
      .action-row { justify-content: flex-start; width: 100%; }
      .select-wrap, select { min-width: 100%; }
      .summary-filter-head { align-items: flex-start; flex-direction: column; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="mainPage" class="page active">
    <div class="wrap">
      <section class="hero">
        <h1>2025년 We'll CSU 전공체험 운영 결과(학과 안내용)</h1>
        <p>만족도조사 중 기타의견이 있는 경우만 의견 반영</p>
      </section>

      <section class="grid-kpi">
        <div class="card kpi-card clickable" id="openSummaryPage" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-label="전체 요약 표 보기">
          <div class="kpi-label">전체 운영회차</div>
          <div><span class="kpi-value">53</span><span class="kpi-unit">회</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card kpi-card"><div class="kpi-label">참여 고교</div><div><span class="kpi-value">45</span><span class="kpi-unit">개 고교</span></div></div>
        <div class="card kpi-card"><div class="kpi-label">참여 학생</div><div><span class="kpi-value">7,596</span><span class="kpi-unit">명</span></div></div>
        <div class="card kpi-card"><div class="kpi-label">총 강좌 수</div><div><span class="kpi-value">386</span><span class="kpi-unit">강좌</span></div></div>
        <div class="card kpi-card"><div class="kpi-label">참여 학과</div><div><span class="kpi-value">51</span><span class="kpi-unit">개</span></div></div>
      </section>

      <section class="section-grid-2">
        <div class="card">
          <h2 class="section-title">학과 선택 및 한 줄 요약</h2>
          <div class="select-row">
            <div class="select-wrap"><select id="deptSelect"></select></div>
            <div class="subtle">드롭다운 선택 시 아래 모든 지표와 의견이 해당 학과 기준으로 갱신됩니다.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="summary-box">
            <div class="summary-item">
              <div class="summary-label">학생들이 가장 좋게 본 점</div>
              <div class="summary-text" id="bestSummary"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="summary-item">
              <div class="summary-label">2026 보완 필요 포인트</div>
              <div class="summary-text" id="needSummary"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h2 class="section-title">학과 참여 결과</h2>
          <div class="metric-pair">
            <div class="metric-card">
              <div class="label">운영 회차</div>
              <div class="value" id="operationCount">0</div>
              <div class="meta" id="operationMeta"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="metric-card">
              <div class="label">참여 학생 수</div>
              <div class="value" id="studentCount">0</div>
              <div class="meta" id="studentMeta"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="compare-wrap">
            <div class="compare-item">
              <div class="compare-head"><span>학생 수</span><span id="studentCompareText"></span></div>
              <div class="compare-track"><div class="compare-fill" id="studentCompareFill"></div></div>
              <div class="compare-meta"><span>0</span><span>평균 166.9명</span><span>평균의 2배</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="compare-item">
              <div class="compare-head"><span>운영 회차</span><span id="operationCompareText"></span></div>
              <div class="compare-track"><div class="compare-fill" id="operationCompareFill"></div></div>
              <div class="compare-meta"><span>0</span><span>평균 7.5회</span><span>평균의 2배</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section-grid-2 equal">
        <div class="card positive-panel">
          <h2 class="section-title">주요 긍정 의견</h2>
          <div class="theme-grid" id="positiveThemeBars"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card negative-panel">
          <h2 class="section-title">주요 개선 의견</h2>
          <div class="theme-grid" id="negativeThemeBars"></div>
          <div class="suggest-box">
            <div class="suggest-title">2026 반영 포인트</div>
            <div class="suggest-text" id="actionPoint"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section-grid-2 equal">
        <div class="card positive-panel">
          <h2 class="section-title">좋았던 점</h2>
          <div class="subtle" id="positiveCountText"></div>
          <div class="comment-top3" id="topPositiveComments"></div>
          <div class="comment-list" id="allPositiveComments"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card negative-panel">
          <h2 class="section-title">아쉬운 점</h2>
          <div class="subtle" id="negativeCountText"></div>
          <div class="comment-top3" id="topNegativeComments"></div>
          <div class="comment-list" id="allNegativeComments"></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bottom-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h2 class="section-title">운영 횟수 기준 상위 10개 학과</h2>
          <table>
            <thead><tr><th>순위</th><th>학과</th><th style="text-align:right;">운영 회차</th><th style="text-align:right;">학생 수</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody id="top10Body"></tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <div class="card overall-positive-card">
          <h2 class="section-title">만족 테마 포인트</h2>
          <div class="subtle">전체 프로그램에서 반복된 긍정 포인트</div>
          <div class="theme-point-list" id="overallPositiveThemes"></div>
          <div class="small-note">전체적으로 전공·진로 정보 제공, 이해하기 쉬운 설명, 흥미·재미 요소가 반복적으로 확인되었습니다.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card overall-negative-card">
          <h2 class="section-title">개선 테마 포인트</h2>
          <div class="subtle">2026 설계 시 공통적으로 검토할 포인트</div>
          <div class="theme-point-list" id="overallNegativeThemes"></div>
          <div class="small-note">2026 설계 시 운영 시간 보완, 체험·실습 확대, 설명 난이도·내용 보완을 공통 검토 포인트로 반영할 필요가 있습니다.</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="footer-message">2025년 전공체험 운영에 수고 많으셨습니다. 2026년도 많은 참여 부탁드립니다.</section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="summaryPage" class="page">
    <div class="wrap">
      <section class="hero summary-hero">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <h1>전체 운영회차 상세 표</h1>
                  </div>
        <div class="action-row">
